UNIT_TESTS

Strange spacing before URLs in plain output:

  udoc is a package to process abstract documents written as  s-expressions 
  (http://people.csail.mit.edu/rivest/Sexp.txt) and produce output in various 
  formats. It is similar to  DocBook (http://www.docbook.org/) but only defines 
  structural, not semantic, elements.

Lack of spacing in ConTeXt output:

  udoc is a package to process abstract documents written as s-expressionsand produce
  output in various formats. It is similar to DocBookbut only defines structural, not
  semantic, elements.

